WEBVTT

01:32.310 --> 01:34.940
[How dare you!?]

01:35.009 --> 01:37.979
[Episode 16]

02:23.840 --> 02:26.350
[Taiji Hall]

02:41.960 --> 02:42.820
Your Highness,

02:43.430 --> 02:45.890
these are all gifts
bestowed by His Majesty.

02:47.280 --> 02:48.470
Just looking at them irritates me.

02:48.470 --> 02:49.680
Her Highness doesn't like them.

02:49.680 --> 02:50.540
Take them away.

02:52.280 --> 02:52.750
Yes.

02:58.030 --> 03:00.090
How on earth did she manage to do that?

03:01.310 --> 03:02.750
I told you long ago—

03:03.120 --> 03:04.590
don't provoke Yu Wanyin.

03:05.000 --> 03:06.660
But you just wouldn't listen.

03:15.430 --> 03:16.750
Your Highness Consort Xie,

03:16.750 --> 03:18.079
you dropped something.

03:24.800 --> 03:25.590
This is a remedy

03:25.590 --> 03:27.240
that His Highness Prince Duan found
for Your Highness.

03:27.240 --> 03:28.350
Take it all at once.

03:28.630 --> 03:30.680
It will take effect within four hours.

03:30.680 --> 03:31.680
But Her Highness has already...

03:31.680 --> 03:32.030
Ling.

03:33.470 --> 03:34.270
Take it for me.

03:36.520 --> 03:37.850
Eunuch, please deliver

03:37.910 --> 03:39.640
a message to Prince Duan for me.

03:40.150 --> 03:41.950
Please tell him to rest assured.

03:45.400 --> 03:47.530
Then this servant will take his leave.

03:52.470 --> 03:53.190
Your Highness,

03:53.190 --> 03:54.470
why didn't you let me tell His Highness

03:54.470 --> 03:56.400
that the matter has been resolved?

03:56.520 --> 03:58.850
Physician Xiao risked his life to save me.

03:58.860 --> 04:00.720
I don't want to drag him into this.

04:02.120 --> 04:02.850
Give me that.

04:15.710 --> 04:16.480
Dan,

04:16.800 --> 04:18.660
today's Grand Longevity Banquet

04:19.040 --> 04:20.190
is so lively

04:20.750 --> 04:22.010
with songs and dances.

04:22.480 --> 04:26.310
The Yan delegation you've been
thinking about has also come.

04:27.480 --> 04:28.560
Are you satisfied?

04:29.190 --> 04:30.790
Mother, you're thoughtful.

04:31.160 --> 04:32.110
I was worried

04:32.630 --> 04:34.159
that if we turned them away,

04:34.659 --> 04:36.260
it would only invite gossip.

04:36.950 --> 04:37.750
And in the end,

04:38.190 --> 04:41.050
it would hurt your reputation as well,
wouldn't it?

04:44.190 --> 04:45.120
In that case,

04:46.159 --> 04:48.430
I should thank you?

04:50.040 --> 04:52.360
My son, you thought of everything.

04:53.360 --> 04:55.090
Whether I'm thorough or not...

04:56.480 --> 04:58.340
I still need to rely on my brother.

05:21.680 --> 05:25.580
[Taiji Hall]

05:24.560 --> 05:26.690
The Yan State delegation has arrived!

05:55.040 --> 05:56.370
He's an expert fighter.

05:56.800 --> 05:57.270
Really?

05:59.860 --> 06:00.330
Mr. Bei,

06:01.120 --> 06:02.800
I'm not really the focus
of tonight's banquet.

06:02.800 --> 06:05.330
You should go watch over
His Majesty instead.

06:06.750 --> 06:09.070
Who knows what unexpected things
might happen?

06:09.070 --> 06:12.120
It's always good to have you
protecting him discreetly.

06:12.120 --> 06:13.010
Mr. Bei, you...

06:18.950 --> 06:20.600
Not even a token protest?

06:22.000 --> 06:23.930
As expected, your mind isn't on me.

06:25.680 --> 06:27.430
I am Haqina, Envoy of Yan!

06:27.830 --> 06:30.070
We wish Your Majesty longevity

06:30.800 --> 06:32.950
and the Empress Dowager good health!

06:33.310 --> 06:36.770
May friendship between our two nations
last for generations!

06:45.560 --> 06:46.600
You've come

06:46.970 --> 06:47.960
from afar.

06:48.360 --> 06:49.120
The journey

06:50.310 --> 06:51.570
must have been tiring.

06:51.720 --> 06:53.120
Thank you, Your Majesty.

06:53.870 --> 06:55.120
At our Emperor's instruction,

06:55.120 --> 06:58.120
we've specially brought dancers
from our country

06:58.240 --> 07:00.410
to perform for Your Majesty

07:00.600 --> 07:02.200
as a token of our good wishes.

07:02.680 --> 07:03.340
Excellent.

07:04.720 --> 07:05.720
Please be seated.

07:05.830 --> 07:07.230
Thank you, Your Majesty.

07:20.680 --> 07:21.270
Yong'er.

07:21.270 --> 07:21.840
Lady Yu?

07:23.480 --> 07:24.940
Why did you arrive so late?

07:27.310 --> 07:28.440
Forgive me, Lady Yu.

07:28.720 --> 07:29.450
My...

07:29.920 --> 07:31.520
stomach has been unsettled,

07:31.750 --> 07:33.430
so I was delayed in my palace.

07:34.800 --> 07:38.930
I haven't yet congratulated you
on regaining your title as Noble Consort.

07:39.920 --> 07:41.430
I don't care about that at all.

07:41.430 --> 07:42.800
When a man loves you,
he wants you to live well.

07:42.800 --> 07:44.430
When he hates you, he wants you dead.

07:44.430 --> 07:44.920
Men—

07:45.800 --> 07:47.730
not a single one of them is any good.

07:58.510 --> 08:00.800
Her Majesty the Empress Dowager specially
bestows upon Your Highnesses

08:00.800 --> 08:03.660
the grape wine brought
by the envoys from Yan State.

08:05.040 --> 08:07.970
-Thank you, Your Majesty.
-Thank you, Your Majesty.

08:46.880 --> 08:47.860
This is so good.

08:48.120 --> 08:49.320
I haven't had enough.

08:53.540 --> 08:54.540
Noble Consort Yu,

08:54.750 --> 08:56.960
this is a very precious wine
bestowed by Her Majesty.

08:56.960 --> 08:57.960
Only one cup each.

08:58.200 --> 08:58.910
You drank hers up...

08:58.910 --> 08:59.640
Why don't you

08:59.960 --> 09:01.490
go complain to His Majesty?

09:06.110 --> 09:06.910
Ms. Tonghao,

09:07.670 --> 09:09.120
I was ill a few days ago.

09:09.800 --> 09:11.510
My stomach hasn't fully recovered,

09:11.510 --> 09:13.110
so I really shouldn't drink.

09:15.720 --> 09:18.210
Her Majesty was also very concerned

09:18.320 --> 09:20.240
about Your Highness's vomiting last time.

09:20.240 --> 09:21.630
She asked me to summon
the most experienced physician,

09:21.630 --> 09:23.870
Physician Zhang,
from the Imperial Medical Bureau.

09:23.870 --> 09:25.430
After the banquet ends,

09:26.120 --> 09:28.690
I'll bring him to examine you again.

09:29.670 --> 09:30.840
Your Highness Noble Consort Yu,

09:30.840 --> 09:32.370
please return to your seat.

09:32.750 --> 09:34.440
Mind the protocol.

09:42.200 --> 09:44.510
Power-abusing wretch.

10:10.910 --> 10:13.270
They say everyone from Yan State
is skilled at dancing.

10:13.270 --> 10:15.730
Their reputation is indeed well-deserved.

10:16.440 --> 10:18.500
Though they are stunning beauties,

10:19.080 --> 10:22.480
they still can't compare to
Beautiful Lady Shanyi back then.

10:23.120 --> 10:23.790
Indeed.

11:25.080 --> 11:25.550
Bravo!

11:26.440 --> 11:28.520
Truly, you're beauties

11:28.630 --> 11:29.920
with exotic charm!

11:30.670 --> 11:31.600
Mr. Wang,

11:31.870 --> 11:34.480
the delegation from Yan State
has come from afar

11:34.480 --> 11:36.270
to present dances
for His Majesty's birthday.

11:36.270 --> 11:37.730
Does the Ministry of Rites

11:37.870 --> 11:39.800
have no reciprocal gift prepared?

11:42.960 --> 11:44.790
Your Majesty the Empress Dowager,

11:44.790 --> 11:47.510
the Imperial Music Bureau
has specially prepared a musical pageant

11:47.510 --> 11:49.170
to present to the delegation.

11:50.910 --> 11:52.120
A musical pageant?

11:53.120 --> 11:54.720
Then what are we waiting for?

11:55.080 --> 11:55.840
Begin.

11:56.960 --> 11:57.360
Yes.

13:13.370 --> 13:16.060
[Zhaluowahan, Emperor of Yan]

13:14.000 --> 13:15.930
Zhaluowahan is the Emperor of Yan,

13:16.480 --> 13:18.750
sinister and cunning behind his smile.

13:27.600 --> 13:29.940
This is clearly mocking our country.

13:30.550 --> 13:32.680
A man can be killed but not humiliated.

13:33.480 --> 13:35.630
Even if we are at odds with our Emperor,

13:36.510 --> 13:39.670
it's not for these Xia people
to mock us so casually.

13:41.270 --> 13:42.300
Can't you see

13:42.720 --> 13:44.380
they're trying to provoke us?

14:00.960 --> 14:01.390
Bravo!

14:01.840 --> 14:02.500
Excellent!

14:04.320 --> 14:05.780
Your Majesty the Emperor,

14:06.270 --> 14:07.930
we people of Yan love dancing!

14:08.790 --> 14:10.880
May we join in?

14:11.440 --> 14:12.100
Certainly!

14:12.630 --> 14:14.240
Joy shared is joy doubled.

14:14.550 --> 14:16.070
I'll beat the drum for you myself!

14:16.070 --> 14:17.470
Thank you, Your Majesty!

14:30.000 --> 14:31.330
Keep the music playing!

14:31.480 --> 14:32.680
Keep the dance going!

14:51.320 --> 14:52.180
Your Highness,

14:52.240 --> 14:54.030
you've already taken the medicine
that Physician Xiao prescribed.

14:54.030 --> 14:56.360
You must not take any other medicines now.

14:58.320 --> 15:01.200
Physician Xiao's medicine won't
take effect for another three days.

15:01.200 --> 15:02.730
But the Empress Dowager...

15:03.030 --> 15:06.080
will send an imperial physician
the moment the banquet ends.

15:06.080 --> 15:07.010
There's no time.

15:08.640 --> 15:10.010
Your Highness, you mustn't!

15:10.010 --> 15:11.140
Physician Xiao said

15:11.480 --> 15:14.150
all fast-acting medicines are
too harsh on the body.

15:14.150 --> 15:16.130
If anything happens to you,

15:16.230 --> 15:17.840
how am I supposed to go on living,

15:17.840 --> 15:18.700
Your Highness?

15:20.630 --> 15:22.230
Then I'll only take one pill.

15:23.440 --> 15:25.100
If it's not effective enough,

15:25.630 --> 15:26.960
I'll take the other two.

15:27.440 --> 15:28.840
Go find Physician Xiao immediately

15:28.840 --> 15:30.640
and ask him how to counteract it.

15:56.630 --> 15:57.320
Where is Consort Xie?

15:57.320 --> 15:58.200
She just left.

15:58.560 --> 15:59.960
She looked unsteady on her feet

15:59.960 --> 16:00.720
and pale.

16:01.240 --> 16:03.040
Her maid wasn't with her either.

16:04.200 --> 16:04.670
What?

16:10.000 --> 16:12.130
Their dancing isn't that impressive.

16:15.510 --> 16:16.200
Let's split up and search.

16:16.200 --> 16:17.270
But Your Highness, you...

16:17.270 --> 16:18.120
What's there to fear?

16:18.120 --> 16:19.550
Nothing will happen to me.

16:19.550 --> 16:21.240
Finding Xie Yong'er is what matters now.

16:21.240 --> 16:23.500
I'm afraid something will happen to her.

16:51.210 --> 16:51.920
Lord Cao,

16:52.600 --> 16:53.670
let me toast to you.

16:54.320 --> 16:54.890
To you!

16:58.080 --> 16:58.900
Sorry.

17:00.760 --> 17:01.360
Pardon me.

17:11.160 --> 17:12.560
Where's my jade pendant?

17:13.829 --> 17:16.230
Where is the jade pendant
I wear at my waist?

17:22.720 --> 17:24.440
If you suspect him,

17:24.829 --> 17:25.790
just search him.

17:57.140 --> 17:59.000
The jade pendant really is on him!

17:59.220 --> 18:00.020
Quickly check

18:00.270 --> 18:02.200
if we still have our jade pendants!

18:04.790 --> 18:05.550
How strange.

18:06.400 --> 18:07.720
How did the pendant

18:08.770 --> 18:10.960
I wear at my waist end up with this envoy?

18:10.960 --> 18:13.090
Could it be that you stole it when no one

18:13.720 --> 18:14.580
was looking...

18:16.200 --> 18:16.610
I...

18:16.640 --> 18:17.270
I didn't!

18:18.160 --> 18:19.230
You're framing me!

18:19.880 --> 18:20.680
Let go of me...

18:23.690 --> 18:24.960
Your Majesty the Emperor,

18:24.960 --> 18:25.690
we are people

18:25.960 --> 18:27.020
from a humble land.

18:27.400 --> 18:29.600
We've never seen such splendor before.

18:30.350 --> 18:32.680
Perhaps greed momentarily overcame him.

18:32.920 --> 18:34.920
We beg Your Majesty's forgiveness.

18:41.240 --> 18:42.040
Your Majesty,

18:42.720 --> 18:45.050
you must uphold justice for this subject.

18:46.830 --> 18:47.630
Your Majesty,

18:47.830 --> 18:48.490
this person

18:49.030 --> 18:50.960
is yours to deal with as you see fit.

19:01.110 --> 19:02.170
Alright, alright!

19:03.590 --> 19:05.710
It's just a jade pendant.

19:06.400 --> 19:08.810
Why make such a fuss?

19:09.960 --> 19:12.640
Since the envoy likes it,

19:13.640 --> 19:15.080
just gift it to him.

19:15.590 --> 19:17.690
Don't let a small jade pendant

19:18.200 --> 19:21.010
damage the friendship
between our two nations.

19:21.920 --> 19:24.350
Your Majesty the Empress Dowager is
absolutely right.

19:24.350 --> 19:26.240
I was inconsiderate.

19:41.200 --> 19:41.880
Mr. Wang.

19:44.200 --> 19:45.110
Where exactly

19:45.960 --> 19:47.820
did you find the pendant just now?

19:48.160 --> 19:49.090
Inside his robe.

19:49.750 --> 19:50.950
Where specifically?

19:52.000 --> 19:53.200
Where specifically?

19:53.880 --> 19:54.830
The place...

19:56.680 --> 19:57.680
Around his chest.

19:58.960 --> 20:01.110
From what I see,
the Yan delegation's clothing

20:01.110 --> 20:03.110
is designed differently from ours.

20:03.920 --> 20:05.200
Such a small object,

20:05.750 --> 20:07.080
placed inside the robe,

20:07.720 --> 20:09.980
would actually remain
near the chest...

20:11.510 --> 20:12.510
How interesting.

20:13.440 --> 20:13.970
Mr. Wang,

20:15.440 --> 20:16.200
try it.

20:19.790 --> 20:20.250
Well...

20:21.480 --> 20:21.810
Uh...

20:23.510 --> 20:24.070
Uh...

20:36.680 --> 20:37.160
No,

20:37.430 --> 20:38.790
that's not how it was just now!

20:38.790 --> 20:40.070
It was clearly at his chest just now!

20:40.070 --> 20:41.090
How did it suddenly...

20:41.090 --> 20:41.890
Well... um...

20:42.160 --> 20:43.810
No, it wasn't like that just now!

20:43.810 --> 20:45.670
No, it wasn't like that. No, no...

20:50.200 --> 20:52.240
Mr. Wang, there seems to be

20:53.200 --> 20:55.330
something unusual about your sleeve.

20:55.790 --> 20:57.390
I wouldn't want to wrong you.

20:57.920 --> 20:58.450
Quickly,

20:59.000 --> 21:00.510
show it to everyone

21:01.200 --> 21:02.600
to prove your innocence.

21:02.760 --> 21:03.420
Your Maj...

21:07.790 --> 21:08.270
Your...

21:14.160 --> 21:14.840
Just now,

21:15.550 --> 21:16.500
I drank too much,

21:17.110 --> 21:18.370
so my mind was unclear.

21:19.000 --> 21:20.310
Please spare me, Your Majesty.

21:20.310 --> 21:21.510
Please spare my life!

21:21.510 --> 21:22.340
Please!

21:22.640 --> 21:23.240
Fine.

21:25.270 --> 21:26.270
Take Mr. Wang away

21:26.830 --> 21:28.500
and help him sober up.

21:30.110 --> 21:31.160
Your Majesty! Your...

21:31.160 --> 21:32.190
Have mercy, Your Majesty!

21:32.190 --> 21:33.350
Please spare me, Your Majesty!

21:33.350 --> 21:34.950
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

21:35.110 --> 21:36.510
Your Majesty the Empress Dowager!

21:36.510 --> 21:38.110
Empress Dowager, please save me!

21:38.110 --> 21:39.110
Empress Dowager!

21:39.590 --> 21:41.440
Empress Dowager, save me!

21:43.440 --> 21:45.030
Your Majesty is wise.

21:47.070 --> 21:48.590
It was all just a misunderstanding.

21:48.590 --> 21:49.190
Be seated.

21:50.270 --> 21:51.670
Thank you, Your Majesty!

22:03.060 --> 22:03.690
Mother,

22:04.720 --> 22:05.920
allow me to toast you.

22:09.070 --> 22:10.220
You displayed

22:11.030 --> 22:12.560
quite the authority today.

22:14.440 --> 22:15.770
Mother, you flatter me.

22:19.960 --> 22:21.240
You don't

22:22.680 --> 22:24.000
need me anymore.

22:32.920 --> 22:33.880
My son,

22:35.270 --> 22:38.510
you can host
the birthday banquet yourself now.

22:55.920 --> 22:56.650
Where is she?

22:58.110 --> 22:59.910
Where on earth did she run off to?

23:15.040 --> 23:15.890
Yong'er,

23:16.550 --> 23:17.550
are you all right?

23:18.480 --> 23:19.010
I'm fine.

23:21.600 --> 23:22.200
This is...

23:25.440 --> 23:26.100
Don't look.

23:26.270 --> 23:26.930
Don't look.

23:27.550 --> 23:28.500
I'm begging you.

23:28.830 --> 23:29.360
Go now.

23:29.830 --> 23:30.630
Just leave me.

23:34.420 --> 23:36.240
You need to go back
and change your clothes.

23:36.240 --> 23:37.370
Can you still stand?

23:38.960 --> 23:40.110
I can't stand up.

23:42.350 --> 23:42.810
Come on,

23:43.440 --> 23:44.300
I'll carry you.

24:08.960 --> 24:09.880
Why is it you?

24:09.900 --> 24:10.700
Stop talking.

24:10.920 --> 24:12.050
Save your strength.

24:12.410 --> 24:13.810
I'm going to stand up now.

24:37.590 --> 24:38.450
Your Highness,

24:38.590 --> 24:40.320
it's exactly as you predicted.

24:43.960 --> 24:45.790
Proceed to Kunyu Palace!

24:59.640 --> 25:00.700
Where is everyone?

25:00.760 --> 25:01.540
Help!

25:02.920 --> 25:03.400
Maids!

25:07.640 --> 25:08.700
Where is everyone?

25:08.920 --> 25:11.120
Where is everyone? Where did you all go?

25:12.590 --> 25:13.120
Yong'er!

25:13.790 --> 25:14.680
Where is everyone?

25:14.680 --> 25:15.810
Where did you all go?

25:17.590 --> 25:19.320
Who dares make such noise here?

25:20.200 --> 25:21.160
How improper!

25:29.270 --> 25:30.750
Aren't those Consort Xie

25:31.030 --> 25:32.790
and Noble Consort Yu, who left

25:31.130 --> 25:34.990
[Kunyu Palace]

25:33.440 --> 25:34.500
the banquet early?

25:35.830 --> 25:39.070
I've been waiting here for you two
for quite some time.

25:40.350 --> 25:43.810
I happened to encounter Consort Xie
outside the hall just now.

25:44.200 --> 25:45.460
Seeing she was unwell,

25:46.070 --> 25:47.130
I brought her back.

25:47.250 --> 25:50.020
[Kunyu Palace]

25:47.930 --> 25:50.070
There're so many servants in the palace,

25:50.070 --> 25:52.560
and yet you, a noble consort,

25:53.310 --> 25:54.510
had to carry her back?

25:56.590 --> 25:57.200
Enough.

25:58.400 --> 25:59.480
You two,

25:59.960 --> 26:01.790
stop trying to deceive me.

26:03.240 --> 26:03.770
Tonghao,

26:04.440 --> 26:05.070
go and see

26:05.550 --> 26:06.960
what they're up to!

26:07.440 --> 26:08.500
Yes, Your Majesty.

26:23.350 --> 26:24.440
Your Majesty,

26:25.030 --> 26:26.430
there are bloodstains on

26:27.030 --> 26:28.240
Her Highness Consort Xie's skirt.

26:28.240 --> 26:29.380
Bloodstains?

26:29.790 --> 26:30.520
Consort Xie,

26:31.200 --> 26:32.060
what happened?

26:33.110 --> 26:33.680
I...

26:34.550 --> 26:36.510
Perhaps her time of the month came early.

26:36.510 --> 26:37.510
It soiled her hem.

26:37.920 --> 26:39.510
I feared it would be improper,

26:39.510 --> 26:40.530
so I

26:40.750 --> 26:42.080
brought her back alone.

26:42.830 --> 26:43.560
Consort Xie?

26:45.550 --> 26:46.400
Consort Xie!

26:46.750 --> 26:48.350
Lift your head and look at me!

26:51.160 --> 26:52.420
Is that truly the case?

26:55.110 --> 26:56.040
Your Majesty...

26:57.000 --> 26:57.440
I...

27:02.780 --> 27:03.330
Yong'er?

27:03.850 --> 27:04.380
Yong'er?

27:04.640 --> 27:05.370
Xie Yong'er!

27:09.680 --> 27:10.410
Xie Yong'er?

27:14.310 --> 27:15.110
Your Majesty,

27:15.310 --> 27:17.510
Her Highness Consort Xie has awakened.

27:17.750 --> 27:18.830
How is Consort Xie?

27:19.400 --> 27:21.560
Her Highness has deficient kidney qi.

27:22.030 --> 27:23.760
Her pulse is weak and unstable.

27:23.830 --> 27:26.030
And she experienced massive bleeding.

27:26.030 --> 27:27.090
It appears to be...

27:28.000 --> 27:28.860
a miscarriage.

27:28.960 --> 27:29.820
A miscarriage?

27:30.110 --> 27:30.510
Quick,

27:30.750 --> 27:32.010
go inform the Emperor!

27:32.070 --> 27:32.400
Yes.

27:34.110 --> 27:34.480
Wait!

27:35.550 --> 27:37.640
Didn't an imperial physician say before

27:37.640 --> 27:39.550
that Consort Xie was not pregnant?

27:39.550 --> 27:40.000
Yes,

27:40.400 --> 27:42.000
Physician Xiao did say so.

27:43.800 --> 27:44.260
Well...

27:44.920 --> 27:45.590
Perhaps

27:46.680 --> 27:48.070
the pregnancy was too early,

27:48.070 --> 27:49.670
so her pulse was not obvious.

27:50.060 --> 27:52.330
This subject only inferred it

27:52.880 --> 27:54.280
from her other symptoms.

27:54.800 --> 27:55.660
What symptoms?

27:57.590 --> 27:58.990
Her Highness Consort Xie

27:59.550 --> 28:01.520
appears to have taken...

28:02.240 --> 28:03.410
an abortifacient.

28:03.920 --> 28:04.980
An abortifacient?

28:09.350 --> 28:09.750
Leave.

28:10.830 --> 28:11.440
Yes.

28:22.310 --> 28:23.200
Consort Xie,

28:23.540 --> 28:25.730
you have quite the audacity!

28:26.750 --> 28:28.280
The Emperor has few heirs.

28:28.400 --> 28:30.420
We finally had hope of having a prince,

28:30.420 --> 28:33.170
and you dared to
commit such an outrageous act!

28:33.400 --> 28:35.260
I didn't take any abortifacient!

28:35.410 --> 28:38.070
Please investigate thoroughly,
Your Majesty!

28:38.510 --> 28:39.310
Your Majesty,

28:39.920 --> 28:41.140
I was hoping

28:41.510 --> 28:43.110
to give you another grandson

28:43.480 --> 28:45.310
to keep the little prince company.

28:45.310 --> 28:47.840
How could I possibly
take any abortifacient?

28:48.090 --> 28:49.190
Oh, Your Majesty,

28:49.960 --> 28:51.220
perhaps it was because

28:51.880 --> 28:53.520
I vomited in public,

28:54.270 --> 28:56.340
making people think I was pregnant.

28:56.640 --> 28:58.040
Someone became jealous,

28:58.720 --> 28:59.830
so...

29:00.480 --> 29:01.590
You mean

29:02.400 --> 29:03.960
you were drugged.

29:15.880 --> 29:16.640
Tell me,

29:18.120 --> 29:19.520
who drugged you?

29:21.890 --> 29:23.160
I don't know.

29:24.640 --> 29:26.040
Is it that you don't know,

29:26.110 --> 29:27.640
or that you dare not say?

29:29.680 --> 29:30.140
Tell me!

29:43.350 --> 29:45.110
Why are you looking at me?

29:48.790 --> 29:49.790
Noble Consort Yu?

29:49.920 --> 29:51.130
It seems this matter

29:51.680 --> 29:53.690
has everything to do with you.

29:54.240 --> 29:55.640
How could it possibly be me?

29:55.640 --> 29:56.770
If not you, then who?

29:57.590 --> 30:00.310
You previously sent someone
to assassinate Consort Shu,

30:00.310 --> 30:02.720
and now you've drugged Consort Xie!

30:03.200 --> 30:06.000
You'll stop at nothing
to win the Emperor's favor!

30:06.310 --> 30:08.910
All my son's affection for you
has been wasted!

30:09.110 --> 30:09.620
Guards!

30:10.000 --> 30:10.410
-Yes!
-Yes!

30:10.410 --> 30:12.010
Seize this demonic consort!

30:12.270 --> 30:13.340
It wasn't me!

30:14.030 --> 30:14.940
Say something!

30:17.270 --> 30:19.470
Why is Your Majesty so certain it was me?

30:19.680 --> 30:21.010
If I really did drug her,

30:21.110 --> 30:22.570
why would I bring her back?

30:22.590 --> 30:24.400
Wouldn't it be better to leave her there?

30:24.400 --> 30:26.550
You were just trying to cover your tracks!

30:26.550 --> 30:28.160
I just came out of the Cold Palace.

30:28.160 --> 30:30.400
How could I have had the chance
to drug her?

30:30.400 --> 30:32.730
Perhaps the real culprit is someone else!

30:38.440 --> 30:39.880
Say something!

30:43.270 --> 30:44.670
My stomach hurts so much.

30:49.680 --> 30:51.850
I haven't eaten anything today.

30:52.680 --> 30:53.680
Like Consort Xie,

30:54.270 --> 30:56.680
I also only drank the cup of wine
that Ms. Tonghao brought.

30:56.680 --> 30:58.490
Why is my stomach cramping too?

31:00.570 --> 31:01.450
Your Majesty,

31:02.030 --> 31:02.510
please

31:03.030 --> 31:04.310
seek justice for Consort Xie and me!

31:04.310 --> 31:05.070
Your Highness!

31:05.070 --> 31:06.190
Your Highness!

31:06.440 --> 31:08.440
You cannot wrongly accuse this lowly maid!

31:08.440 --> 31:10.000
Your Majesty, please be fair!

31:10.000 --> 31:12.290
This maid did nothing!

31:12.510 --> 31:14.160
This maid would never dare!

31:14.960 --> 31:17.180
This maid would never dare!

31:24.240 --> 31:26.040
Your Highness, are you alright?

31:26.890 --> 31:27.820
It hurts so much!

31:29.400 --> 31:31.260
Your Highness, please slow down.

31:34.880 --> 31:35.740
Your Highness,

31:36.030 --> 31:37.690
the Empress Dowager has left.

31:39.400 --> 31:40.110
Turn around.

31:40.110 --> 31:42.240
Let's go settle this with Xie Yong'er.

31:58.240 --> 31:59.100
Your Highness,

31:59.330 --> 32:00.590
the medicine is ready.

32:00.790 --> 32:01.650
Please take it.

32:06.480 --> 32:08.030
The medicine was prepared
by Physician Xiao.

32:08.030 --> 32:08.890
It's very safe.

32:15.510 --> 32:17.310
Has the fetus been taken care of?

32:17.880 --> 32:19.670
I found a tree far away

32:20.350 --> 32:21.260
and buried it there...

32:21.260 --> 32:22.060
Don't tell me.

32:29.680 --> 32:30.540
Your Highness.

32:37.310 --> 32:38.480
Do you know, Ling?

32:46.030 --> 32:48.270
I used to think I was the chosen one,

32:49.830 --> 32:51.630
and that with the script in hand,

32:51.880 --> 32:54.610
I could change the course
and everything myself.

32:56.480 --> 32:58.610
But in the end, I couldn't do anything.

33:01.880 --> 33:04.270
I couldn't even protect my own child.

33:07.270 --> 33:08.560
I've failed myself.

33:09.960 --> 33:11.280
I've failed him too.

33:12.310 --> 33:14.570
No, Your Highness. Don't think that way.

33:15.240 --> 33:16.880
There are many people you've failed,

33:16.880 --> 33:18.210
but he's not one of them.

33:18.270 --> 33:19.550
Please calm down, Your Highness.

33:19.550 --> 33:20.720
Her Highness Consort Xie is ill...

33:20.720 --> 33:22.000
Chu Qi, take Ling out.

33:22.000 --> 33:22.310
Yes.

33:25.550 --> 33:26.320
Let's go.

33:29.110 --> 33:31.480
You also suspect
Prince Duan is full of lies, don't you?

33:31.480 --> 33:34.280
Otherwise, why do you keep
making excuses for him?

33:35.720 --> 33:37.050
What about Prince Duan?

33:37.720 --> 33:39.430
I know everything about you two.

33:39.430 --> 33:41.630
How long are you going to keep hiding it?

33:42.720 --> 33:44.160
I don't know what you're talking about.

33:44.160 --> 33:45.970
You were almost dead.

33:46.070 --> 33:48.330
Are you still going to deceive yourself?

33:53.310 --> 33:54.110
Let me ask you:

33:54.400 --> 33:56.310
the new Commander of the Imperial Guards,

33:56.310 --> 33:57.110
Zhao Wucheng—

33:57.240 --> 33:58.100
whose man is he?

34:01.160 --> 34:03.030
Even the Imperial Guards
protecting the entire Imperial City

34:03.030 --> 34:04.890
are under Prince Duan's command.

34:04.920 --> 34:05.960
How could he fail to protect

34:05.960 --> 34:07.360
your small Kunyu Palace?

34:07.550 --> 34:10.400
Was he truly powerless,
or did he do it deliberately?

34:10.400 --> 34:12.600
Don't you know the answer in your heart?

34:14.840 --> 34:17.570
He keeps saying he loves you
and will protect you.

34:18.000 --> 34:19.110
But when you were carrying his child,

34:19.110 --> 34:20.800
he gave you no protection at all.

34:20.800 --> 34:22.030
If that wasn't using you as bait

34:22.030 --> 34:23.480
to divert the Empress Dowager,

34:23.480 --> 34:24.409
then what was it?

34:32.630 --> 34:33.480
If you don't believe

34:33.480 --> 34:35.810
that Yu Wanyin would say such things
to Xie Yong'er,

34:35.810 --> 34:36.540
that's fine.

34:39.360 --> 34:41.020
Let me ask you as someone else.

34:46.280 --> 34:46.679
How...

34:47.590 --> 34:48.000
are...

34:49.070 --> 34:50.469
you? [spoken in English]

34:51.630 --> 34:52.230
Answer me!

34:53.190 --> 34:54.989
How are you? [spoken in English]

35:01.740 --> 35:03.570
Zhang San's Diary.

35:03.670 --> 35:05.150
I've caused you all to be punished.

35:05.150 --> 35:07.030
I feel terrible about it.

35:08.190 --> 35:08.670
Today,

35:09.510 --> 35:11.550
I've specially invited you all here,

35:11.550 --> 35:12.810
hoping these pastries

35:13.320 --> 35:14.520
might make amends.

35:24.920 --> 35:25.720
Crown Prince,

35:25.880 --> 35:27.320
what's the meaning of this?

35:27.320 --> 35:28.920
This is rotten swill for pigs!

35:28.920 --> 35:30.380
Do you take us for beggars?

35:35.480 --> 35:36.610
This is impossible.

35:40.230 --> 35:40.840
I didn't!

35:46.550 --> 35:47.150
Come here!

35:47.710 --> 35:49.160
They were perfectly good pastries
just moments ago!

35:49.160 --> 35:51.070
How did they become rotten scraps?

35:51.070 --> 35:53.000
I watched them being put in myself!

35:53.070 --> 35:53.630
Speak!

35:54.190 --> 35:56.050
Please calm down, Your Highness!

35:56.150 --> 35:57.550
This servant did follow

35:57.550 --> 35:59.110
Your Highness's instructions.

35:59.110 --> 35:59.980
You're lying!

36:00.510 --> 36:02.220
Who put you up to framing me?

36:02.360 --> 36:03.000
Tell me!

36:03.320 --> 36:04.800
Please calm down, Crown Prince.

36:04.800 --> 36:06.960
This eunuch's offense
doesn't warrant death.

36:06.960 --> 36:08.820
Please show mercy, Crown Prince.

36:20.710 --> 36:21.970
So it was him.

36:33.760 --> 36:35.560
Since this is your kind gesture,

36:36.190 --> 36:36.630
I shall

36:37.070 --> 36:38.360
accept it

36:38.800 --> 36:39.590
on behalf of all the other princes.
